interfaces

Interface User

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    UserImpl

    public interface User
    This interface specifies a User that is known to a Calendar instance. The user has a name, an unique email address and an URI which allows setting up a connection to him. Please note that a User is managed by a Calendar instance, it can not be created or deleted without it; if it was removed from a Calendar, the User instance becomes invalid and should not be user anymore.
